# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented here.<br>
This project uses [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).

---

## [Debug-v1.6.0.1_083125] – 2025-08-31
### Added
- JSON Project file support (`.jfpp`)
    - Proper Banner region saving
- Legacy Project file support (binary serialization `.fppj`)
    - Legacy Project files are converted upon saving
    - Legacy Project files Banner region still default to USA
    - Adjusting the region & saving the project(converts) will allow for loading & storing the Banner region correctly
- `Genre` field
- `Genre` field autofill, & 'Flash' genre autofill for `WiiWare Flash injects`
- Support locally saving downloaded WAD bases & Banner images
- Flash Operation Manuals (WIP, roughly 60%?)
- JP-specific `00.app` banner file for Flash injects (WIP)
- MIDI support for Kirby TV (experimental, untested)
- Dropbox WAD download support
    - Support for `Flash Base ’25` & `KirbyTV (by idkwhereisthisname)`
- Friish + WiiMart logo assets.

### Changed
- Updated `banner.ini` for Flash injects
- Improved 4-char TID randomizer
    - Checks existing TIDs in WiiMart
    - Fetches the proper Region suffix
    - Fetches the proper Platform prefix
- Refactored Flash Base handling
- Removed Region locks on various Platforms

### Fixed
- Saving/loading of project Banner Region
- Kirby TV (EUR), added Kirby TV (USA)
- Background color for Kirby TV
- SWF frame rate handling (`update_frame_rate = 0`)
- Config & `banner.ini` defaults for Flash injects
- Bug with `not_copy` always off
- Various `database.json` additions & corrections
- defaults in `Settings.cs` for Flash injects

---
